nodes.text: Linjak Mosa was a male Kadas'sa'Nikto who lived during the waning years of the Republic Classic era. In 32 BBY, he was wanted by Jabba the Hutt for destroying several of the crime lord's spice freighters. His bounty, worth 6,000 credits alive and 3,000 credits dead, was claimed by Jango Fett.
